rows.label: tlk45350171_03_msg0001
rows.name:
There's no point staying here in Acedia.
Not now that Fan-sama is gone.

rows.label: tlk45350171_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm going to leave my work here
to a colleague and head on back
home to Superbia.

rows.label: tlk45350171_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh, Fan-sama... Why do I still visit
the cathedral, knowing I will never
see you there again?
